  "name": "Focused Hearing-Aid",
  "type": "feat",
  "_id": "XMwiAOITTdUdvOAt",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Clans/Otogi.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You afix a blinking device to your ear or around your head, enhancing your perceptive abilities. Increase your passive perception by +5 and the range of your blindsight by +10 feet. You cannot be surprised against creatures within range of your blindsight. As an action, you can spend a charge to dilate your senses for 1 minute, focusing on a single creature, doubling the range of your blindsight but only allowing you to sense a single target with it at a time. The creature you sense this way cannot gain the benefit of being hidden from you. For the next minute, as a bonus action you can declare a new target for your blindsight.</p>",
